    "html":  "\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-bottom:24px;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#60a5fa; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.8px; margin-bottom:6px;\"\u003eDaily Economic Briefing\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003ch2 style=\"margin:0; font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#e2e8f0;\"\u003eWednesday, 24 June 2026\u003c/h2\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;\"\u003e\n    \u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.25); color:#34d399; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eMOVE 64.05 Compressed\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.25); color:#34d399; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eSOFR 3.58% Healthy\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(96,165,250,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.25); color:#60a5fa; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eNFCI \u0026#8722;0.514 Loose\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(248,113,113,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.25); color:#f87171; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003e5Y Auction 13:00 ET\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"background:#1a1f2e; border:1px solid #2d3748; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:20px;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#94a3b8; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.6px; margin-bottom:14px;\"\u003e\u0026#128202; Liquidity \u0026amp; Stress Metrics \u0026#8212; The \u0026quot;Gnosis\u0026quot; Pulse\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:12px; color:#64748b; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:14px;\"\u003eCurrent regime: Structural Expansion, with the draft framing this as the peace-dividend extension. Bond volatility is highly compressed while secured funding and broad financial conditions remain loose.\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"overflow-x:auto;\"\u003e\u003ctable style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;\"\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #2d3748;\"\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eMetric\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:right; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eValue\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eMarket Context\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:center; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eStatus\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;\"\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0; font-weight:500;\"\u003eMOVE Index\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:right; color:#34d399; font-weight:700;\"\u003e64.05\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:left;\"\u003eTerm premium is flattened and rate-vol protection is cheap after the post-FOMC and post-geopolitical-risk unwind.\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:center;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.25); color:#34d399; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eHighly Compressed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;\"\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0; font-weight:500;\"\u003eSOFR Rate\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:right; color:#34d399; font-weight:700;\"\u003e3.58%\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:left;\"\u003eWholesale funding remains stable, keeping the interbank liquidity floor intact into today\u0026apos;s data and auction windows.\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:center;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.25); color:#34d399; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eHealthy\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0; font-weight:500;\"\u003eNFCI\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:right; color:#60a5fa; font-weight:700;\"\u003e\u0026#8722;0.514\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:left;\"\u003eThe Chicago Fed index remains deep in loose territory, supporting credit availability and systematic equity exposure.\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:center;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background:rgba(96,165,250,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.25); color:#60a5fa; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:6px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"\u003eLoose\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"margin-top:16px; padding:14px 16px; background:rgba(96,165,250,0.06); border-left:3px solid #60a5fa; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:#60a5fa; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.6px; margin-bottom:6px;\"\u003eGnosis Interpretation\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:13px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;\"\u003eThe liquidity stack remains an equity-supportive structure: MOVE at 64.05 shows premium extinction, SOFR at 3.58% shows clean funding, and NFCI at \u0026#8722;0.514 shows credit conditions still loose. Pullbacks are more likely mechanical order-flow resets than structural risk-off unless these inputs deteriorate.\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"background:#1a1f2e; border:1px solid #2d3748; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:20px;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#94a3b8; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.6px; margin-bottom:14px;\"\u003e\u0026#128197; Economic Calendar: 2026-06-24\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"font-size:12px; color:#64748b; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:14px;\"\u003ePrimary-source check: Census lists May New Residential Sales at 10:00 ET, EIA\u0026apos;s weekly petroleum release is scheduled for 10:30 ET, and TreasuryDirect lists the 5-Year Note auction for today. The draft housing item was corrected from continuous follow-through to the official release window.\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"overflow-x:auto;\"\u003e\u003ctable style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;\"\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #2d3748;\"\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eEvent\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:center; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eEST (US)\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:center; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eGMT+8 (Local)\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:center; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eImportance\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;\"\u003eNotes\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;\"\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0;\"\u003eUS May New Home Sales / New Residential Sales\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:center;\"\u003e10:00\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:center;\"\u003e22:00\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:center;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:#f87171; font-weight:600; font-size:12px;\"\u003eMedium-High\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#64748b; font-size:12px;\"\u003eOfficial Census calendar confirms the May 2026 release. Watch absorption, months\u0026apos; supply, and rate sensitivity across builders.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;\"\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0;\"\u003eEIA Weekly Petroleum Status Report / Crude Inventories\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:center;\"\u003e10:30\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:center;\"\u003e22:30\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; text-align:center;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:#f87171; font-weight:600; font-size:12px;\"\u003eMedium-High\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#64748b; font-size:12px;\"\u003eEnergy inventory shock window. A crude draw or product tightness can briefly challenge the disinflation narrative.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#e2e8f0;\"\u003eUS 5-Year Note Auction\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:10px 12px; color:#94a3b8; text-align:center;\"\u003e13: